description:
Sigil presents: ELECTRIC SWEAT
This historic genre is finally receiving the love it deserves at Valhalla, 18th July. Pioneered by legends such as Kraftwerk, Afrika Bambaata and Grandmaster Flash, Electro has taken countless forms since it's inception. We've curated a lineup of artists to explore and showcase a range of sounds with their roots in electro. Expect Ghettotech, Volt, Miami Bass, and both classic and modern Electro.
Featuring:
@its_jay.luv (Christchurch)
@jason_o_c (vinyl set)
@doobiedenize
@nymph.loads
@stacey.leeeee
Poster by @stacey.leeeee x

Doors at 9pm  |  Tickets $8 for UTR
